{"type": "article", "id": 22119, "title": "在家办公？这些方式让你的小天地更好看", "description": "一些简单的小 tips，或许能给你带来灵感。", "date": "2016-02-14T07:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8483, "name": "办公空间"}, {"id": 9835, "name": "地毯"}, {"id": 23267, "name": "中性色调"}, {"id": 23268, "name": "绿色植物"}, {"id": 23269, "name": "花朵"}], "category": 17, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 479, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702111311ZTtOlGc45K8iy1MJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">对于很多有机会在家办公（或者学习）的人来说，伏案工作的那一块桌、满当当的书橱可能就是自己最重要的一方天地。可能是很多人除了床以外用去最久时光的地盘，值得认真对待，而不是随便找个什么角落，放台电脑就好。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">怎么看起来舒心又兼顾功能性呢？这里的一些小 tips 或许能给你灵感。</p>\n<p class=\"\">白色色调总是最经典的选择，看起来整洁高效，未经粉饰的白墙、简单的白色桌椅就能达到效果。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111258R0wNy9APhurf2HZI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26557864\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111259VPaTFMZSmt8LlEO5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70779977\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">但如果觉得视线内只剩下白色太过严肃，添加灰色、米色、原木色的中性色会挺和谐，比如桌椅、窗帘、台灯等物品。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111259snkud6GwfKpEMeBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113006YURu58IdBOaEK2V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">有时候一样的空间靠一块不同风格的地毯感觉就大有不同：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111300d6yzDqUgh8AeorBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>别忘了好看对健康也有益的绿色植物和花朵，这是空间扮靓的利器。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111301NGDo0z9dUxhIAVLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111302yALQaouW0OwKbvpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">在整体很素净的地方，其实像文件夹、收纳盒可以采用亮眼的颜色来增添一些有趣的细节。我们之前<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/21406.html\">介绍过一些颜色好看设计经典的桌面文具、办公用品</a>，挑选一套喜欢的颜色就是最简单的装饰。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111302pmZ1vi8T62EANKIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111303ZPeYbhOkRDaF81dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">当然还有些人更喜欢颜色跳跃、明亮的空间，感觉那些更有活力，更能激发灵感，那么墙壁、桌椅、橱柜、地板都可以换上鲜艳颜色。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111303sA2ryxwpuJd130Tt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75591532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113049UCoywk2FGxzp1QZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75278121\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">再轻柔一些的粉红和粉蓝也很不错，前者看起来很温暖，后者则带来舒缓和平静。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111304lFRkmPIbaZ936vNg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">墙面也要好好利用起来，不仅能节省空间，也减少了墙原本的单调。带孔的面板和支架可以随意固定很多东西，还有各式“口袋”，装基本杂志和小花都挺好看。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113059nGrF5P1ZMLpm0Vd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">关于墙上的收纳，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17821.html\">我们也有过介绍</a>。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111305jxVKmgPwhNQ3poAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61167002\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113068x5DtGBvyQOIWwXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61728395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">或者准备一块板子，既可以写上你最喜欢的一句格言，也可以贴满照片，或是最有用、最具纪念意义的单据、纸条粘起来。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111306vTnYUqRZbHe3joKM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111307pmc9oMByfrkw31YI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111307Ovfi3VGpXTmR1onq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75621891\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">说到照片的话，就不得不提强大的照片墙和画框，几乎屡试不爽。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113080dBILfUYbTXxWQG5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78682171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113085BVipbhLTUHg9eQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">还有些利用好角落的典范，折叠的或是角落里的桌板</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021113096BYIRbNz9oE0JpCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111309G7iD4HrBcOtdNQ0u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111309ZGQFeRHJ94so8Sz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">很多时候，书架上满满的书就是最好的装饰。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111310zI9uqDU74BcdePOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75154512\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">当然，对于这样的一个空间，放松的内容也是要有的，来个简易的小推车，放点酒水、小吃和杂志什么的，看起来很惬意。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111311CrGu1yToSgY9vzmt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n"}